Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.11,0:01:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到换班时间了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.67,0:02:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.87,0:02:02.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭候多时了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.33,0:02:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一目标 镇压完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.53,0:02:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.88,0:02:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是相当无趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.31,0:02:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是「那个」圣地的警备吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.88,0:02:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其说是警备 不如说是用来监视牵制他国的摆设吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.93,0:02:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且换岗人员的生活设施 全都在圣地里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.41,0:02:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说只要潜入了内部 其余的就是小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来这应该是最困难的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.88,0:02:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉哟 第二、第三目标也镇压完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.28,0:02:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此下去 不就可以把全部的警备所都镇压了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然也可以 但圣机师为数不多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.71,0:02:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要这么多茧也没用处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.49,0:02:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且被修利冯注意到就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.33,0:03:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边的警备是完全独立的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来爱美拉去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.31,0:03:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种帮不上忙 又啰里啰唆的人不在不是更好么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.72,0:03:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.65,0:03:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她去解决我的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微借用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔的走狗竟擅自使唤别人的属下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不晓礼数呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦 那还真抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是你这 看来很顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.48,0:03:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第四、第五、第六目标 镇压完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 你就在一旁好好看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs30}校译：胖子 无尽空寂 始&终の零 润色：马甲雷 时间：Xelloss
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs80\fn方正粗宋_GBK\pos(640,520)\fad(500,0)\shad1\bord1\be1}袭  来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.64,0:03:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于今日的来临
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.94,0:03:51.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本人衷心致谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.18,0:03:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理想并非空谈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:03:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行动必得实施
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.85,0:04:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不失其意义
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.31,0:04:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诸位的各项努力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将引领我们通往新生纪元
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望诸位谨记于心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久后我军主力就会到达
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.13,0:04:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.15,0:04:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位出发吧 让此刻成为我们庆祝胜利的清晨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.38,0:05:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警备所被...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.05,0:05:17.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得多赚点印象分才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.07,0:05:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利利索索地一个个收拾掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们知道我们的厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:26.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.13,0:05:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种东西会有用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么 如果离开水线会变回茧的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.21,0:05:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊...是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么声音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.29,0:05:51.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪音？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.15,0:05:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特雷尤正在...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:05:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆炸后的浓烟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.61,0:06:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是警备所那边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:02.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警备所？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:05.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么警报没有拉响
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各地警备所 已排除近七成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 很不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.15,0:06:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.58,0:06:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在这里干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这究竟是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是让圣地由我支配而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.38,0:06:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.39,0:06:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特雷尤的旗舰要塞！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个控制室也由我掌控了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部乖乖投降的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:53.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切 那老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由她去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.73,0:06:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是这边 修利冯的圣机人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？藏了两台啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来解决 其他的交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.81,0:07:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 中央控制室被占领了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.42,0:07:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅斯特家的小鬼也摆出一幅自大的拽样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 知道了 马上过去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.01,0:07:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以为占领了那里就能支配一切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.18,0:07:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人笑掉大牙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.20,0:07:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那面具女说的风暴难道是指这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.94,0:07:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岂止是风暴 简直是台风
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:35.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的巴巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.96,0:07:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎样让巴比伦穿过那么狭窄的溪谷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:41.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉夏拉殿下 学院长来电联络
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:46.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先能简洁说明一下目前所发生的状况吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.37,0:07:49.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也应该了解我在斯特雷尤的处境吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对天地神明发誓 这件事跟我毫无关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.59,0:07:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的情况必须让全校人员去避难
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能提供协助吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.86,0:08:02.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还用说吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学院长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.51,0:08:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 白鸟城立刻准备出发
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.03,0:08:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.65,0:08:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去协助引导学生避难和抵御敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.50,0:08:17.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一个人去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣地的教职人员已开始进行避难引导了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.41,0:08:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现今闯入圣地的可是斯特雷尤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.47,0:08:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在此时不做点事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.53,0:08:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的立场就很不利了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.03,0:08:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们家的训示是自己的事情自己做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.72,0:08:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你即使不肯替我出这个头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.27,0:08:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就权作是报答那些平日对你爱护有加的人也行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我立刻就去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.57,0:08:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我走着瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯雅 你也跟剑士一起...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.47,0:08:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.29,0:09:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然袭击我们的是斯特雷尤...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.92,0:09:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是达古麦亚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.51,0:09:04.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉夏拉殿下请尽快...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.01,0:09:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯雅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.93,0:09:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想和他一起的话 那就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是避难
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第七目标已攻陷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.81,0:09:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.22,0:09:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.31,0:09:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制突然...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.52,0:09:33.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经足够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.39,0:09:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面差不多也乱作一团了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微去整点儿零用钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.72,0:09:47.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦乌 瓦乌 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.17,0:09:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.76,0:09:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是外面好像很混乱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个借我用用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:09:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？先别着急
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:09:59.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边的武器马上就装好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这台足矣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东西装太多会影响机动力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据小岚的情报 这里好像是圣机工的工房
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.91,0:10:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没值钱的东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦乌 这家伙的反应变得更灵活了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.37,0:10:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来这些不都是之前偷袭疗养地的山贼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.29,0:10:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦乌 这俩家伙交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.42,0:10:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎～啊 等等 剑士 你要去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥拉殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑精灵的负面时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.39,0:10:42.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和平常比起来真像完全变了个人似的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.17,0:10:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.39,0:10:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用不着这么害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.43,0:10:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会对你很温柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:10:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐东西 那家伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！你在抓着哪里啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别乱动啊 要掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我宰了你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一点 就够着...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真抱歉剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.19,0:11:44.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次都让你看到我不成体统的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.77,0:11:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要没受伤就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:49.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,负面时间真是可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.19,0:11:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再抱久一点也行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.70,0:11:53.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是大好时机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.22,0:11:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个赶紧去确认是否有没来得及避难的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.42,0:11:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦！电灯泡马上消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.18,0:12:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑士阁下 公主就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:06.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下 请一定努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这俩家伙 我要扣他们薪水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 实战起来貌似也没什么了不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.90,0:12:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 真卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.21,0:12:31.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍伊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.24,0:12:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是反抗我们的下场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.30,0:12:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.25,0:12:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.87,0:12:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑精灵领域很麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽快解决掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙没有武装吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.74,0:13:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,防卫机能启动了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我们去确保避难学生的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.27,0:13:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.53,0:13:41.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰外各处中弹 但损伤轻微
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:43.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人炮台陆续出现
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.07,0:13:47.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭他们已经做的很不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让圣机人全体出击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.13,0:13:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让这些家伙妨碍巴比伦的前进路线
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴巴隆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.26,0:13:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈伯尼瓦的芙罗拉女皇传来通信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.46,0:14:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴巴隆卿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.14,0:14:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对圣地进行军事侵犯 到底有何目的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来此处的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道了又能怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.47,0:14:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想阻止我的话 就用实力来说话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.76,0:14:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您这么说...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.63,0:14:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真让我感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.39,0:14:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为在圣地开战 若没有一些大义作口实可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.62,0:14:32.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴巴隆大人 前方有巨大的物体靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.52,0:14:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全炮门展开完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射击开始～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.95,0:15:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 奉陪到底
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 真是好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.39,0:15:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是华丽的登场呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边也能接收避难学员与教职人员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请将通道打开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真帮了大忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.03,0:16:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点 小心圣机人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这边 请快些！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:14.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 好危险哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.96,0:16:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽缇亚会长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:34.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽缇亚会长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这很危险 请别这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:40.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为大家争取点避难时间 我还能做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双方数量太悬殊了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:47.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 学生会长想登上圣机人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.97,0:16:51.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 会长大人也想跟我们玩玩么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.06,0:16:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微吓吓她们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:16:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽缇亚会长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你个卑鄙小人 难道不觉得羞耻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许用那种臭屁的口气跟我们说话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.06,0:17:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉碧丝快跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.74,0:17:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要 我要保护丽缇亚会长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.67,0:17:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈哈 自己找死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 那个是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:32.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是剑士 那个碍眼的侍从
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.88,0:17:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 真是得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.25,0:17:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧 拉碧丝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.49,0:17:46.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 丽缇亚会长没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.49,0:18:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 快起来 抓住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.63,0:18:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别哭了 拉碧丝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会痛扁他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.82,0:18:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥拉殿下 这台机工人交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.07,0:18:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪里 野生动物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.39,0:18:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙落荒而逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.57,0:18:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.67,0:18:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斗技场的防御体系相当健全
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣机人越不过埃纳的水线 这里很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.01,0:18:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各班长确认人员的数量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认结束后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.00,0:19:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1班到4班从地下16号通道搭乘教会战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.43,0:19:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5班到8班从29号通道前往拉夏拉殿下的白鸟城
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9班以后从7号通道进入芙罗拉殿下的装甲列车
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.93,0:19:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清楚各自去向就开始行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.07,0:19:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那按照学号排列好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葛丽姆跟普露是8 伊丽丝拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是真的吧 达古麦亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.38,0:19:41.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道总有一天会变成这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅塞亚老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是拉夏拉殿下的护卫骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而他是梅斯特家族的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.81,0:19:56.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事...我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.94,0:20:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅塞亚老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各班级全部到齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家按顺序兵分三路经地下通道避难了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.23,0:20:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报告辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:12.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个也快去避难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑士？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底想干什么啊 那个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.22,0:20:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被大家稍微捧高些就自以为了不起似的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.99,0:20:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但毕竟只是个侍从
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.51,0:20:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岂能与我们男圣机师相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.53,0:20:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.15,0:20:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.46,0:20:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 打中了 打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:05.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本区域没落下什么人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.54,0:21:07.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲大人真够呛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.34,0:21:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在圣地开着装甲列车和巨型战舰火拼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.13,0:21:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是前所未闻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.38,0:21:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 雪音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.12,0:21:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,达古麦亚大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.93,0:21:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.77,0:21:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是 剑士？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:29.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他究竟想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.42,0:21:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 那家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.26,0:21:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.20,0:21:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑士同学
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.51,0:22:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.78,0:22:02.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.25,0:22:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.24,0:22:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学员和职员总计1149人 均于白鸟城得到妥善保护
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.42,0:22:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人员健康状态良好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.80,0:22:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,负伤者也仅为轻伤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.42,0:22:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.39,0:22:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.68,0:22:48.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若就此让两人一同见鬼去就谢天谢地了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.64,0:22:51.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两方都活力十足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.90,0:22:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 那到底是...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.22,0:22:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.53,0:22:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然都怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.81,0:22:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个啊 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.95,0:23:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑士先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.96,0:23:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.54,0:23:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉夏拉殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.06,0:23:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.64,0:23:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是...什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.10,0:23:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说 那是光之属性
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.08,0:23:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光之属性？×2
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.04,0:23:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教会秘藏的古代文献中曾提到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.84,0:23:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为光所笼罩之人拯救世界 为暗所笼罩之人毁灭世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.02,0:23:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为暗...所笼罩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.61,0:24:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有就是光与暗表里一体
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.42,0:24:08.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光或许会转为暗 反之亦然
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.36,0:24:12.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然是白色的圣机人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.33,0:24:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.81,0:24:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然那时的圣机人驾驶员是剑士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.36,0:24:23.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣机师？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.04,0:24:26.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是我们的剑士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.84,0:24:48.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能 才一转眼就...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.81,0:24:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊 谁来救救我啊啊啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.72,0:25:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 不要背对着那家伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.96,0:25:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失吧 从我的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.27,0:25:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.93,0:25:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,达古麦亚大人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.74,0:25:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.21,0:25:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦乌安丽 去掩护他
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.84,0:25:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在没那个空闲
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.47,0:25:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢货 正中下怀 收拾掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.79,0:26:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 在那里面的话
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.86,0:26:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一对一倒也罢了 敌人若以众欺寡的话可十分不利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.33,0:26:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里是被石柱和埃纳水线环绕的牢笼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.42,0:26:20.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.48,0:26:24.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.18,0:26:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅塞亚姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.41,0:26:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这林立的石柱里 机动性无法得到发挥
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.96,0:26:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.43,0:26:40.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.47,0:26:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混账
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.26,0:26:46.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从左右迂回包抄
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.78,0:26:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.58,0:27:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往你的方向去了 科露蒂涅
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.41,0:27:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 来吧 老娘会好好疼爱你的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.05,0:27:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在这里起跳
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.40,0:27:25.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.84,0:27:37.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...小鬼...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.96,0:27:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.83,0:27:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁啊？那个圣机人的驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.32,0:27:58.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从没见过纯白的圣机人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.34,0:28:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.17,0:28:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那正是我们的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.95,0:28:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柾木剑士同学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.39,0:28:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？ 剑士同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.99,0:28:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉夏拉殿下随从的那位？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.56,0:28:10.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是圣机师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.02,0:28:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乘上茧时 是我亲眼所见的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.66,0:28:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说那白色圣机人是剑士在驾驶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.37,0:28:17.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 剑士小弟？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.89,0:28:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.30,0:28:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 是剑士同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.27,0:28:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个柾木剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.21,0:28:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如你所见
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.09,0:28:32.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在林立的石柱与水线的环绕下战斗极为困难
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.46,0:28:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.39,0:28:35.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过真有那么难吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.69,0:28:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傻小子
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.32,0:28:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.29,0:28:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽有众多已至达人境界的圣机师们在此斗技场中战斗过
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.81,0:28:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还没有谁能完成那样的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.03,0:28:56.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超乎想像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.66,0:28:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.35,0:29:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,达古麦亚 此时应选择暂时撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.22,0:29:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡说什么 怎能因为那家伙而退兵
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.42,0:29:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.64,0:29:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藏到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.92,0:29:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克里夫
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.16,0:29:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混账
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.28,0:29:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反倒是我们自投罗网 被诱入了他的狩猎场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.92,0:30:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母后大人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.83,0:30:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦你了 雪音妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.91,0:30:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你保护玛丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.58,0:30:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岂敢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.44,0:30:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来吃惊的事还真多
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.15,0:30:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到剑士是圣机师
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.40,0:30:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.34,0:30:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.32,0:30:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还拥有那么强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.46,0:30:25.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次可要找拉夏拉好好地询问详情才行
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.41,0:30:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.51,0:30:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了剑士 敌人的圣机人近乎全军覆没
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.47,0:30:36.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应可迫使斯特雷尤就此撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.16,0:30:37.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还真不好说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.63,0:30:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.65,0:30:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎还备有后手呢 巴巴隆卿
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.44,0:30:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.99,0:30:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴比伦 到达目标
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.80,0:30:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰身控制 误差修正
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.79,0:31:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结界确认 构造检查 扫描开始
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.69,0:31:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反结界阵 开始构筑
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.65,0:31:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.07,0:31:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道巴巴隆的目的是...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.01,0:31:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.26,0:31:39.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.00,0:31:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,达古麦亚
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.63,0:31:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.61,0:31:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 科露蒂涅还...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.31,0:31:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老妈的话她自己会有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.08,0:32:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对这种怪物我能有什么办法啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.64,0:32:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 梅塞亚姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.51,0:32:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 我的声音难道你听不见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.40,0:32:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回答我啊 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.24,0:32:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久违了 凯亚
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.76,0:32:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.59,0:32:23.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.89,0:32:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快你就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.06,0:32:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.96,0:32:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣机神的台座...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.10,0:32:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅塞亚姐
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.88,0:32:45.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.06,0:32:49.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结界解析完成 开始侵入
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.75,0:33:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.25,0:33:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.90,0:33:16.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 觉醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.82,0:33:20.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.22,0:33:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯亚 梅塞亚其实并非你的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.44,0:33:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅塞亚是你父亲在遗迹中与圣机神一同被发掘出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.60,0:33:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先史文明所创造出来的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.80,0:33:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.49,0:33:40.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不信就看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.49,0:33:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.14,0:34:08.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多...露...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.12,0:34:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.16,0:34:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.60,0:34:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接通教皇大人的直通专线
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.71,0:34:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟有此事
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.34,0:34:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万分之一机率的事态被触发了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.81,0:34:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴虐之神复活的时候到了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.62,0:34:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.01,0:35:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快带领大家去避难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.95,0:35:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不想让她们陪葬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.94,0:35:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 梅塞亚姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.79,0:35:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要去 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.05,0:35:35.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.83,0:35:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.54,0:35:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 仅靠圣机人有这能耐 当真了得
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.09,0:35:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里很危险 快去避难
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.90,0:36:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做好最后的确认后也会离开
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.66,0:36:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎能留下你在这里...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.63,0:36:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能丢下那个傻小子和姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.69,0:36:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你一定要平安归来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.94,0:36:23.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 这样就结束了...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.97,0:36:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔？怎么了？攻击啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.30,0:36:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么对剑士下不了手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.79,0:36:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受梅塞亚的人格影响？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.99,0:36:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.32,0:36:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我不能拒绝命令
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.60,0:36:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.83,0:36:44.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,细胞组织的劣化似乎比预想的还要糟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.08,0:36:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯雅小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.08,0:36:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有落单的学生了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.59,0:36:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也差不多该去避难了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.09,0:36:53.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是剑士先生还...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.35,0:36:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经没什么能做的了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.62,0:37:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扰敌之类的工作还能做到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.25,0:37:03.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾 被对方当成目标会很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.70,0:37:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 我们很可能会拖剑士的后腿
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.41,0:37:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退吧 那白痴的话没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.21,0:37:17.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.02,0:37:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.68,0:37:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒醒吧 梅塞亚姐
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.50,0:37:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的 剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.09,0:37:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅塞亚跟我已经融合了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.12,0:37:32.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我记得 在这里和你一同经历过的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.50,0:37:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五花八门的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.60,0:37:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话 请你把那些忘掉 那我就感激不尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.94,0:37:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然的确是很愉快的场所
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.02,0:37:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我已无法继续待在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.06,0:37:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 剑士 能到我的身边来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.33,0:37:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里没有我的容身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.94,0:37:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反倒是多露 来我们这边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.58,0:38:02.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的容身之所我会帮你开拓的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.28,0:38:06.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.72,0:38:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.58,0:38:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗才是我存在的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.63,0:38:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是为此而被制造出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.61,0:38:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样就满足了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.73,0:38:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是命运
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.11,0:38:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.94,0:38:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学院长 已确认全部学生避难完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.17,0:38:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 那么准备出发
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.53,0:38:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.97,0:38:34.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您没事吗 奥拉殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.21,0:38:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,损害状况呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.59,0:38:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了剑士 全都获救了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.43,0:38:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那么立刻出航
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.57,0:38:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙罗拉殿下 来列车避难的学生已全部收容完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.82,0:38:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽有数人受伤 但221人均平安抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.33,0:38:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.32,0:39:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主炮发射准备
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.56,0:39:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母后大人 剑士先生还在战斗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.33,0:39:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢 但应该不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.78,0:39:13.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 雪音妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.86,0:39:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主炮发射准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.85,0:39:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员撤退完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.10,0:39:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指挥车辆撤退到安全区域
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.62,0:39:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主炮发射后让前方车辆自爆
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.95,0:39:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切顺利的话应该能阻止敌人追击哦
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.76,0:39:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅塞亚姐
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.57,0:39:45.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.97,0:39:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.79,0:39:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛利亚大人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.18,0:39:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我母后现在要做蠢事了 请回避！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.15,0:39:53.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.18,0:40:19.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.28,0:40:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.40,0:40:41.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅塞亚姐
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.02,0:40:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是无计可施啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.08,0:40:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算想夺回圣地 我们连像样的战斗力都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.40,0:40:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么去结界工房吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.73,0:40:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.67,0:40:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「如果万一圣机神启动的话 就来我这里 」
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.99,0:40:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乌奈瓦师傅这么说过
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.87,0:40:59.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.49,0:41:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚯嚯
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.73,0:41:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你差不多该把你知道的全都说出来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.15,0:41:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 但是在那里之前
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.59,0:41:12.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑士 去迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.49,0:41:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 哦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.24,0:41:19.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组织严重劣化 剑士的力量太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.52,0:41:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还能战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.86,0:41:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连变型都没戏了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.04,0:41:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.77,0:41:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.91,0:41:27.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我按
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.72,0:41:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙罗拉你个大姨妈
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.28,0:41:51.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个没常识的中年女人
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.35,0:41:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把我们都卷进去的话可怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.03,0:41:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正得救了 就随她去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.87,0:41:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果OK怎样都行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.67,0:42:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.18,0:42:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易收集的水晶全都落下了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.40,0:42:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～费了好大的功夫的说...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.89,0:42:11.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.95,0:42:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的确已约法三章不许再挖水晶的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.78,0:42:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于这事 必须给我老实交代！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.45,0:42:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.79,0:42:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没危机感的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.95,0:42:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,达古麦亚 作战算是成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.29,0:42:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无须如此沮丧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.62,0:42:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.38,0:42:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别太勉强自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.62,0:42:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一次我可不一定在你身边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.94,0:43:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.90,0:43:06.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟预期一样在潜伏中
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.55,0:43:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边的准备也很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.58,0:43:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.83,0:45:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为惹麻烦的只有巴巴隆而已
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.40,0:45:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 先去奥拉的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.49,0:45:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 异世界的圣机师物语
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.73,0:45:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「思绪」
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.75,0:45:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次一定要清算那笔旧帐
